Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:01.72,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Hello, Touko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.10,0:00:03.45,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Hello, Lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:07.05,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Okay, from today we’re going to really tackle what’s bothering you, Lain-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:08.33,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:09.34,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I mean Lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:12.50,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,We’re going to try to figure things out so you don’t see nightmares anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:17.68,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I haven't seen nightmares much lately. Sometimes I hear things, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:19.96,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Hear things? Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.29,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.17,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,It sounds like someone talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.62,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t like hearing it, so I try my best to ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:31.00,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Hmm. Do you know whose voice you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.17,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don’t know. It can be a man’s voice or a woman’s voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:39.93,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Where do the voices seem to come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.13,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,From the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.94,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,The sky? From what part of the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:49.22,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,From the electric lines. Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:56.02,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,The electric lines... Do you know what’s inside of electric lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.86,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Wiring that carries electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:06.64,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Right. They carry electricity that comes from power plants. Do feel like you sense electricity?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.22,0:01:13.82,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I don't really know. Sometimes it seems to come from the sky; not the electric lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:16.65,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Are you bothered by it right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:21.64,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,No. I’m not scared now. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.96,0:01:26.24,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,When you told your mother, did she tell you not to tell anyone else about these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:27.46,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:32.46,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,People who don’t hear these things would think strange things about you if you told them, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:35.78,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You don’t have to worry about telling me anything you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.25,0:01:37.37,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You don’t have to worry, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.54,0:01:40.06,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m not going to think strange things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.70,0:01:41.73,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Because I’m sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:49.04,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,No, Lain. Let’s see. You know about "sleep paralysis"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.45,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Is it when a demon comes out and you can’t move your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:55.12,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Right. Have you ever had that happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:56.70,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:57.97,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It was frightening, wasn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:01:58.89,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Uh, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:00.78,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you know why sleep paralysis happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.12,0:02:02.10,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.34,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,The human body is very mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:13.08,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,When you’re sleeping, there are times when your mind is awake, and times when your body is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:14.09,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.89,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:20.57,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Well, that’s good enough for now. What parts of you are awake right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:22.36,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Both?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:23.06,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:29.10,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Suppose I said something really scary right now, and you felt scared enough to run out of this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:30.44,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,What would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.29,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Run out of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:33.02,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.09,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Suppose that you feel so scared that you want to run out of this room, but your body is asleep and you can’t move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.06,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,That's what sleep paralysis is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:45.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,So if you’re having a nightmare but your body is asleep and you can’t move, you are having sleep paralysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.13,0:02:46.78,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.22,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you know what’s involved, it’s not so scary, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.38,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,No. It isn’t.
